            &lt;div class=&quot;comment-body js-comment-edit-hide&quot;&gt;

                &lt;span class=&quot;comment-copy&quot;&gt;Also, using &lt;code&gt;parseInt()&lt;/code&gt; is not recommended. Try &lt;code&gt;parseInt(&quot;025&quot;);&lt;/code&gt; and it &lt;i&gt;will&lt;/i&gt; fail.&lt;/span&gt;

